\\"Despite missing out on a gold medal, Helen Glover was delighted her team \\\"raced with so much heart.\\\"\", \"from\": 3765, \"to\": 3866, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3804, \"end\": 3816, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Helen_Glover_(rower)\", \"score\": 0.9968858553495725, \"rank\": 0.0031234382808593376, \"text\": \"Helen Glover\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Helen_Glover_(rower)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Helen_Glover_(rower)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u2764\\ufe0f#Olympics#Paris2024#BBCOlympicspic.twitter.com/uEDHfaxa7g- BBC Sport (@BBCSport)August 1, 2024Glover, however, did not seem to mind that the focus had been shone on her life as a mum, referring to it in her post-race chat with BBC Sport.She said of the race: \\\"We put it all out there.\", \"from\": 3867, \"to\": 4153, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4097, \"end\": 4100, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"score\": 0.99999999833517, \"rank\": 1.009327387078362e-09, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We raced the plan we wanted to race; we raced together with so much heart.\", \"from\": 4154, \"to\": 4228, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There can not be regret looking back and knowing you did all you can.\", \"from\": 4229, \"to\": 4298, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"To have their three little faces beaming big smiles after seeing their mummy compete on the world stage, I am really proud of that.\", \"from\": 4298, \"to\": 4430, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I hope for mums this sends the message that you can go back to whatever you want to do and be exceptional, not despite of having children but because you have children.\\\"\", \"from\": 4430, \"to\": 4600, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In what was a nail-biting 